Class AggregatingListener<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.ForwardingListener<T,List<T>>
      • uk.co.strangeskies.utilities.AggregatingListener<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of event to listen for
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Consumer<T>, Observable<List<T>>

    public class AggregatingListener<T>
extends ForwardingListener<T,List<T>>
    An implementation of ForwardingListener which aggregates consumed data into a list, then provides it to listeners in chunks of all remaining data.
